#: .\effects.json
msgid "Wasted"
msgstr "烂醉如泥"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Wasted'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You tried 'Uncle Ben's Mustang' moonshine. You feel like you died, "
"resurrected and then died again."
msgstr "你尝试了'本叔叔的野马'私酿酒。感觉像是死了一次，复活后又死了一次。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Wasted'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel AWFUL."
msgstr "你感觉糟透了。"

