#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid ""
"So, you are that new student I was told about? Unfortunately for you, I know"
" everything about you. I think you understand that you are not the first "
"person this old fool sends to us. But you're in luck, today I'm in a good "
"mood, and I'm ready to give you a chance to redeem yourself. Bring that old "
"man's head and I'll think about giving you a chance to join my school."
msgstr ""
"所以，你就是那个我听说过的新闻学？不幸的是，我对你的一切了如指掌。我想你明白，你不是那个老糊涂派来的第一个人。但你很走运，今天我心情不错，准备给你一个赎罪的机会。把那老家伙的头带来，我会考虑给你一个加入我流派的机会。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
#: .\npc\Teachers\police_teacher.json
msgid "I'll think about that."
msgstr "我会考虑的。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "I think we should fight."
msgstr "我觉得我们应该打一场。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "I'm still waiting."
msgstr "我还在等着。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "I'm already on it!"
msgstr "我已经在做了！"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Here it is."
msgstr "给你。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Actually, let's fight!"
msgstr "其实，我们来打一场吧！"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid ""
"Very well. Consider that you have received my trust. If you still want to "
"become a student of my school, come to me when you have free time."
msgstr "很好。就当是你获得了我的信任。如果你还想成为我门派的弟子，有空时来找我吧。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Thank you for your trust."
msgstr "感谢你的信任。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "We do this easy way or a hard way?"
msgstr "我们是要来软的还是来硬的？"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Easy way, please."
msgstr "请来软的。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Hard way, please."
msgstr "请来硬的。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Bend over."
msgstr "趴下。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "Oh noes!"
msgstr "哦不！"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "So be it!"
msgstr "那就这样吧！"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
#: .\npc\Moneylender_hub\moneylender.json
msgid "Let's rock!"
msgstr "让我们摇滚起来！"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
msgid "I hope you bring me something worth my attention."
msgstr "我希望你能带来值得我关注的东西。"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
#: .\npc\Moneylender_hub\bartender.json .\npc\Refugee
#: center\NPC_Barry_Button.json center\NPC_Berry_Button.json
#: .\npc\Teachers\boxer_johny.json .\npc\Teachers\dojo_blackbelt.json
#: .\npc\Teachers\drunken_master.json .\npc\Teachers\hobo_victoria.json
